explanations.description: Proper nouns, specifically locations (e.g. cities, countries) and names of individuals, as well as some common nouns related to food (e.g. falafel) and social classes (e.g. bourgeois), and terms related to social attitudes (e.g. homophobic) and emotions (e.g. inspired).
